{"tid":1817884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈 手快有手慢冇]小薯茄情人節見面握手會跳樓價$600","createTime":"2020-01-09T12:28:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T18:37:23.000Z","uid":14812,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"093fd443d10ba0432947d5bbd180507009ffb1a9","tid":1817884,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:28:56.000Z","msg":"【召喚單身狗🐶💓 】<br />\n單身狗們有冇發現可怕嘅情人節嚟緊？💕💕但唔使驚！小薯茄幫你安排咗活動－－小薯茄 x Breakup Tours 2月14單身狗圍爐取暖之夜！🔥🔥❣️❣️<br />\n<br />\n除咗任飲任食打邊爐之外，仲有精彩豐富節目內容：程人富大數婚禮禁忌、阿J單身之道、冰童Turn You On、破冰遊戲、麗英新歌發布等等等等，仲有「回禮禮『襪』」畀你有機會識到同場嘅朋友仔！<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年2月14日（星期五）<br />\n時間：晚上七時入席<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣新新酒家<br />\n人數：約240人<br />\n衣著：婚宴裝（著靚少少就得㗎啦）<br />\n價格：<br />\n單身赴會1人門券-港幣600元<br />\n二人同行2人門券-優惠價港幣1,111元<br />\n（另外只要加多200元，就可以有一個 *活動限定記念品「小薯茄限定 &mdash; 失戀急救包」）<br />\n<br />\n想參加嘅小薯茄快啲即刻download Breakup Tours個app報名，然後搵埋單身朋友仔一齊嚟參加啦！<br />\n等緊你哋！準時入席！<br />\n已經有得報名啦：<a href=\"https://app.breakuptours.com/VhF9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.breakuptours.com%2FVhF9&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF00uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=aba4cce8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://app.breakuptours.com/VhF9</a><br />\n詳情可以入返Breakup Tours嘅App睇清楚！<br />\n<br />\n*活動限定紀念品「小薯茄限定 &mdash; 失戀急救包」，包括【小薯茄限定款「Snapney」一次性菲林相機】、【內含麗英原創歌曲的音樂扣針播放器】，以及一份「神秘額外獎賞」，有機會是免費台北來回機票。<br />\n<br />\n無論你失戀暗戀無人戀，乜戀都好<br />\n2月14，小薯茄陪你圍爐取「戀」<br />\n<br />\n程人富 Laiying エミー TANG 鄧麗英 JefferyKwan - 阿J 阿冰 - PingpingNg 童童<br />\n<br />\n#breakuptours #214 #singlevalentines #單身狗圍爐取暖之夜 #單身狗 #情人節 #圍爐 #Pomato #小薯茄 #上埋YouTube睇其他片啦 <br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n快啲上埋我哋YouTube睇吓啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/cdCiUR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FcdCiUR&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF00uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=e8fa7f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/cdCiUR</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有呀！上埋我哋Instagram，可以睇到小薯茄嘅日常生活㗎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/pomatohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpomatohk%2F&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF00uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=1e46b14d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/pomatohk/</a><br />\n<br />\n入嚟 蕃茄薯仔湯 個Group，仲有好多幕後花絮㗎！"},{"pid":"bb5ce4f28e4cabf54bbea987039fc537cca5e964","tid":1817884,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:30:32.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3faee9481c0f266a980e31682d8a55a8b46f967","tid":1817884,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb5ce4f28e4cabf54bbea987039fc537cca5e964","tid":1817884,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:30:32.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:32:22.000Z","msg":"波台好多A0狗 俾少少面黎ok?"},{"pid":"bb54b2643d2119c7c1cd1ce1f5933f716e67715d","tid":1817884,"uid":32577,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />情人節水鳩情侶洗錢都算<br />\n宜家毒撚都要俾你撚"},{"pid":"f1f3b70b4154abb6fcbf0cb2c9fc26c445548e26","tid":1817884,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99c09787757061c56e3ef2e59b796d5112c7c55","tid":1817884,"uid":59101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:34:04.000Z","msg":"唔好玩鳩啲毒撚啦<br />\n仲要600<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff5bb1de58542d07c43e04f26d270bd15677514","tid":1817884,"uid":207122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"咁嘅垃圾活動收六百<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我捐左去好過"},{"pid":"1b90f61c7aad552833cb2dec6a7e4a16c6f4eca6","tid":1817884,"uid":14812,"like":3,"dislike"